    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition and has been maintained to the highest possible standards. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless paintwork to the immaculate interior, looks and feels brand new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a smooth engine and precise handling that reflects its low mileage and careful ownership. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that is essentially in 'as-new' condition.",
